son-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/krayzie-bone-Scott-Dudelson-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/krayzie-bone-Scott-Dudelson-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/krayzie-bone-Scott-Dudelson-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/krayzie-bone-Scott-Dudelson-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-1" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block">来自开创性嘻哈乐队<a href="/artists/bone-thug-n-harmony" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="internalLink" data-ordinal="1">Bone Thugs-N-Harmony</a>的<a href="/artists/krayzie-bone">Krayzie Bone</a>因肺部动脉出血而入院治疗。</div><div class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block">该团体的经理鲍比·迪周一向<a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/music/story/2023-09-25/krayzie-bone-hospitalized-bone-thugs-n-harmony" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="externalLink" data-ordinal="2"><em>《洛杉矶时报》</em></a>证实了这一消息。不过，他没有说明这名 50 岁的男子被送入该设施的原因。</div><div class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block">据<em><a href="https://allhiphop.com/news/krayzie-bone-bone-thugs-n-harmony-hospital/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="externalLink" data-ordinal="1">AllHipHop 报道</a></em>，Krayzie Bone（真名 Anthony Henderson）在上周五（9 月 22 日）开始咳血后住进了医院。</div><div class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block">据报道，医生在指示亨德森进行 CAT 扫描后，发现他的一个肺部有一条出血动脉。结果，他立即接受了手术并戴上了呼吸机。 </div><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Bone Thugs N Harmony - 十字路口" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VMYAEHE2GrM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>周一， <em><a href="https://www.tmz.com/2023/09/25/krayzie-bone-thugs-n-harmony-hospitalized-coughing-blood-fighting-life/?adid=social-tw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="externalLink" data-ordinal="1">TMZ</a></em>透露，Krayzie Bone 被置于诱导昏迷状态，以“帮助愈合过程”，因为动脉仍在流血。该出版物透露，这位格莱美奖获奖说唱歌手计划再次接受手术以修复血管。</p><p> Layzie Bone 在他、Wish Bone、Flesh-n-Bone 和 Krayzie Bone 的照片下写道：“在这个充满挑战的时刻，当我的直系暴徒和 Bone 暴徒家族团结在我兄弟身后时，我们谦卑地要求获得片刻的隐私。” Instagram。 “我们一家人正以力量面对Krayzie Bone的意外住院，你们的祈祷是希望的灯塔。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CxqGuG7LTkm/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.