 《反恐精英2》将惩罚与作弊者交往的玩家https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2-will-penalise-players-for-associating-with-cheaters-3506446?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=counter-strike-2-将惩罚与作弊者交往的玩家Imogen DonovanFri, 29 Sep 2023 09:53:20 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3506446 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/counter-strike-2-cheater-associates-will-also-be-sanctioned.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/counter-strike-2-cheater-associates-will-also-be-sanctioned.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/counter-strike-2-cheater-associates-will-also-be-sanctioned-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/counter-strike-2-cheater-associates-will-also-be-sanctioned-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/counter-strike-2-cheater-associates-will-also-be-sanctioned-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/counter-strike-2-cheater-associates-will-also-be-sanctioned-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/counter-strike-2-cheater-associates-will-also-be-sanctioned-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>但目前尚不清楚与作弊者“交往”是什么意思</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2-will-penalise-players-for-associating-with-cheaters-3506446">《反恐精英 2》将惩罚与作弊者交往的玩家的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/counter-strike-2-cheater-associates-will-also-be-sanctioned.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/counter-strike-2-cheater-associates-will-also-be-sanctioned.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/counter-strike-2-cheater-associates-will-also-be-sanctioned-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/counter-strike-2-cheater-associates-will-also-be-sanctioned-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/counter-strike-2-cheater-associates-will-also-be-sanctioned-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/counter-strike-2-cheater-associates-will-also-be-sanctioned-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/counter-strike-2-cheater-associates-will-also-be-sanctioned-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/valve">Valve</a>表示，那些与<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/counter-strike-2"><em>《反恐精英 2》</em></a>作弊者“交往”的人也将受到处罚。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/best-upcoming-games-we-saw-at-gamescom-2023-3505950">以下是我们在 Gamescom 2023 上看到的一些即将推出的最佳游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p>Valve 在周三（9 月 27 日）向<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/steam">Steam</a>发布的<em>《反恐精英 2》</em> <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/730/view/3747614808335403091" target="_blank" rel="noopener">发行说明</a>中表示：“当一名或多名队伍成员被判作弊并被永久封禁时，他们的所有同伙都将受到失去个人资料排名和 CS 评级的惩罚。” 。</p><p>这是关于续集的各种变化的公告，包括新玩家的训练日教程、纠正某些位置的脚步声、将休闲和死亡竞赛地图分成不同的组、玩家模型上的动画眼睛以及最终会掉落的小鸡离开眩晕地图。</p><p>然而，“同事”这个词并没有清楚地说明其含义。可能是一名球员不断地、有意识地与已被证明作弊的人合作，以便在比赛中获得不诚实的优势。 </p><figure id="attachment_3421821" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3421821" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3421821" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-limited-test.jpg" alt="《反恐精英 2》。图片来源：Valve。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-limited-test.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-limited-test-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-limited-test-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-limited-test-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-limited-test-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-limited-test-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3421821" class="wp-caption-text"> 《反恐精英 2》来源：Valve</figcaption></figure><p>如果一名玩家碰巧是作弊团队的一员，尽管他们没有意识到这一点，但希望他们不会陷入开发商制裁的交火中。</p><p>截至撰写本文时，Valve 尚未对与作弊者“关联”的构成做出任何解释。前作<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/counter-strike-global-offensive"><em>《反恐精英：全球攻势》</em></a>多年来一直与作弊作斗争， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-cheating-is-now-under-fbi-investigation-2913455">其中一次升级为联邦调查局的全面调查</a>。</p><p>电子竞技诚信委员会在 2021 年表示，“一小群相对较小但重要的玩家”被指控“在很长一段时间内”“在北美 [激浪联盟] 中组织比赛造假”。</p><p>据称这些事件还涉及“外部博彩集团”，这就是包括联邦调查局在内的多个美国当局介入此案的原因。</p><p>其他游戏新闻方面，Epic Games 宣布本周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/fortnite-developer-epic-games-loses-830-employees-in-layoffs-3506388" target="_blank" rel="noopener">裁员三分之一的游戏开发员工</a>，本轮裁员总计 830 名员工。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2-will-penalise-players-for-associating-with-cheaters-3506446">《反恐精英 2》将惩罚与作弊者交往的玩家的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
