人们利用这种开放性来让我成为我不是的人。”</p><p>与此同时，利佐<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-named-in-new-bullying-and-harassment-lawsuit-from-fashion-designer-3502090">在另一起诉讼中被点名后</a>不久<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-accepts-quincy-jones-humanitarian-award-amidst-ongoing-legal-battles-3502672">就接受了昆西·琼斯人道主义奖</a>，同时发表的演讲似乎提到了她目前的法律麻烦。</p><p>在一份关于最新诉讼的声明中，利佐的发言人声称，该诉讼是“虚假、荒谬的宣传噱头诉讼”，来自一个“从未真正见过利佐，甚至从未与利佐交谈过”的人。</p><p> “我们将给予应有的重视。没有任何。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-asks-judge-to-dismiss-ridiculous-harassment-lawsuit-3506381">利佐要求法官驳回“荒谬”的骚扰诉讼的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 Shed Seven 分享由 Rowetta 主演的新单曲和客串专辑《A Matter Of Time》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/shed-seven-share-new-single-featuring-rowetta-and-talk-guest-heavy-album-a-matter-of-time-3505094?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=shed-seven-share-new-single-featuring-rowetta-and-talk-guest-heavy-album-a-matter-of-timeDamian Jones Fri, 29 Sep 2023 09:00:47 +0000 Music InterviewsMusic NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3505094 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_shedseven_press_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="棚七" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_shedseven_press_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_shedseven_press_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_shedseven_press_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_shedseven_press_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_shedseven_press_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_shedseven_press_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>请观看“In Ecstasy”的视频，主唱 Rick Witter 向 NME 讲述与 Pete Doherty 和 Reverend And The Makers 的 Laura McClure 的合作、两名乐队成员的离开以及摆脱 90 年代“怀旧标签”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shed-seven-share-new-single-featuring-rowetta-and-talk-guest-heavy-album-a-matter-of-time-3505094">Shed Seven 的帖子分享了由 Rowetta 主演的新单曲和客座嘉宾专辑“A Matter Of Time”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_shedseven_press_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="棚七" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_shedseven_press_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_shedseven_press_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_shedseven_press_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_shedseven_press_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_shedseven_press_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_shedseven_press_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shed-seven">Shed Seven</a>分享了他们与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/happy-mondays">Happy Monday</a>实力派<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rowetta">Rowetta 合作的热门新单曲《In Ecstasy》，</a>并向<em>NME</em>讲述了他们如何招募<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-doherty">Pete Doherty</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/reverend-and-the-makers">Reverend And The Makers</a>的 Laura McClure 制作他们的第六张录音室专辑《A Matter Of Time》。首先请观看 NME 上的新视频，以及我们对主唱 Rick Witter 的采访。</p><p>在这首令人振奋的歌曲中，维特和星期一的歌手在强劲、机动的节奏和高亢的吉他声中交换声音。主唱偶然发现了一首他认为最适合 Rowetta 强有力的歌声的旋律后，这首歌就诞生了。</p><p> “当我写那首歌时，一想到这个特殊的旋律，我就想到了 Rowetta，我只是想‘我能听到她唱那首歌’，”他告诉<em>NME</em> 。</p><p> “因为这些年来我们见过几次面，而且我们早在周一就支持过，所以我想我不妨伸出手来看看她是否感兴趣，而且她对此很感兴趣。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="棚七 - 狂喜壮举。 Rowetta（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jA4cILQaYiQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他继续说道：“她就是这么无礼，不是吗？她有曼彻斯特的粗鲁和曼彻斯特的活力。她也没花太多时间就明白我们想要什么。我只是给她看了旋律并说，“这些是歌词，看看你想做什么，在我们意识到之前，她已经大喊（采用她的歌声）：“<em>狂喜</em>！”这非常罗维塔。”</p><p>在去年的 Bingley Weekender 音乐节上，The Shed Seven 的主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-doherty">皮特·多尔蒂 (Pete Doherty)</a>发现<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-libertines">The Libertines</a>乐队的成员在舞台边跟着他们的歌曲一起唱后，他还设法让皮特·多尔蒂 (Pete Doherty) 加入了专辑的最后一首歌曲《Throwaways》。</p><p> “我们在主舞台上在 The Libertines 之前演出，当我们在做我们的布景时，我只是看着舞台的一侧，发现彼得站在那里，我的家人在观看演出，他正在唱每一个字，”Witter记得。</p><p> “所以当我们结束演出后，我走过去，他告诉我，在 90 年代——前浪荡子——他会拿着吉他坐在床上，学习 Shed Seven 的歌曲，我觉得这很酷。我只是说，‘看，我们已经有了这首歌，我们的唱片上还有另外几位嘉宾，我们不妨把船扔到这里，你想跳上来吗？’他说，‘我绝对愿意’。” </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_petedoherty_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">浪子乐队的皮特·多尔蒂 图片来源：Mike Lewis Photography/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>在其他地方，约克乐队招募了 Reverend And The Makers 键盘手和伴唱 Laura McClure 创作歌曲《Tripping With You》，这是一首关于痴迷跟踪者的歌曲。</p><p> “我们想要一个听起来非常甜美和天真的女孩的声音，”维特解释道。 “这些年来我们多次支持牧师，我想到了劳拉。我通过电话与她交谈并向她提供了简报并说这有点跟踪狂。我们想要一个非常天真无邪的人，以至于我想要在那里咯咯地笑。所以她给了我们一些不同的笑声，我为我们选择了正确的笑声，我认为她做到了。”</p><p>在 2022 年 3 月开始的专辑创作之前，长期鼓手艾伦·利奇 (Alan Leach) 和吉他手乔·约翰逊 (Joe Johnson) 离开乐队去追求其他项目。</p><p> “这就是其中之一，不是吗？你无法阻止某人做他们想做的事，”维特推理道。 “这两个人显然觉得是时候尝试做点别的事情了。我们所能做的就是祝愿他们在未来的工作中一切顺利。</p><p> “但我想只要乐队中有我、[贝斯手]汤姆[格拉德温]和[吉他手]保罗[班克斯]，我们就是从一开始就一直存在的中流砥柱。因此，只要人们看着我在舞台上扭动臀部，唱着金色和彩虹，我们就应该感到高兴，不是吗？” </p><figure id="attachment_3506481" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3506481" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3506481" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowetta-live-2023-1.jpg" alt="罗维塔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowetta-live-2023-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowetta-live-2023-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowetta-live-2023-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowetta-live-2023-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowetta-live-2023-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowetta-live-2023-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3506481" class="wp-caption-text"> Rowetta 图片来源：Lorne Thomson/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>两人离开后，乐队招募了前 Audioweb 鼓手 Robert “Maxi” Maxfield 和多乐器演奏家 Tim Wills（此前曾与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ian-brown">Ian Brown</a>合作）录制《A Matter Of Time》，最终他们撤回了乐队。西班牙山脉。在那里，他们与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/killing-joke">Killing Joke</a>贝斯手 Youth 重聚，后者制作了他们 2017 年的专辑《Instant Pleasures》。</p><p> “我们在西班牙他的工作室待了三个星期，在半山腰上租了一辆汽车，他是唯一被允许驾驶这辆车的人。所以我们基本上被困在那里，他是青年人的一股强大的自然力量，”维特说。</p><p>在会议期间，制作人会强迫乐队用原声吉他演奏每首歌曲，而不是听他们的演示。</p><p> “我们发现自己每天早上都必须向他展示我们要录制的下一首歌曲，所以我们基本上每天录制一首歌，”主唱解释道。 “他会说，‘对了，我们今天播放什么歌？’我们用原声吉他弹奏，我唱歌，前一分钟他还望着天空，想知道他到底听到了什么，下一分钟他就会说，“哦，是的，这听起来真的很棒” 。他是一个非常聪明的人，听到他的想法和意见是一个非常有趣的过程！然后我们录音时他就睡着了。” </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_youth_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> 《致命玩笑》制作人兼贝斯手 Martin “Youth” Glover 2023 年 4 月 6 日 图片来源：Lorne Thomson/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>至于他对与新乐队成员合作的想法，维特说：“这太棒了。他们让我们做好了准备，因为他们很饿，他们是新来的，他们希望事情尽可能顺利。所以这给了我们很大的刺激。他们也是出色的音乐家，我们不必两次告诉他们如何做某事。他们只是得到了线索。”</p><p>在过去六年里录制了两张专辑后，维特认为乐队终于摆脱了他所说的 90 年代的“怀旧标签”。</p><p> “我们已经失去了像很多乐队那样出去演奏我们的老热门歌曲的怀旧之情，”他补充道。 “我们发现自己又感觉更时尚了，因为我们正在做全新的事情。事实上，新的东西绝对可以与我们过去的材料相媲美，因为它听起来非常新鲜和流行，这是一件很棒的事情。所以我们发现自己处于一个非常健康的位置。</p><p> “话虽如此，我永远不会厌倦唱我们的老歌，因为房间里看着我们的每个人都在享受最美好的时光。当你看到 2,000 个人看起来都在度过一个非常非常美好的夜晚时，你很难感到无聊。”</p><p>在发行新专辑之前，Shed Seven 将于下个月前往英国进行巡演，他们希望这次巡演能让他们有机会与唱片中的一些客座艺术家一起路试他们的歌曲。</p><p> “不幸的是，当我们进行大部分演出时，罗维塔在澳大利亚。事实证明，她在我们对阵曼彻斯特的前一天就回家了，所以如果我们能让她出来和我们一起在她家乡的舞台上表演，那就太酷了。我们会祈祷她不会太时差反应，”维特热情地说。</p><p> “如果我们在谢菲尔德并且劳拉有空，我们肯定会问这个问题。显然，彼得本人也是个大忙人，但他们总是很受欢迎，我们为什么不呢？另一种选择是买一个大屏幕，让他们在上面唱歌。我们必须跟上时代的步伐，不是吗？”</p><p>至于 2024 年的前景，这位主唱总结道：“我认为这对我们来说将是重要的一年，从我们首张专辑《Change Giver》30 周年纪念第一周发行的全新专辑开始。如果您是七号棚的粉丝，我认为您应该系好安全带，因为您将会享受到愉快的旅程。如果你不是粉丝，就找一块大石头，躲在它后面。”</p><p> 《Matter Of Time》于 2024 年 1 月 5 日发行。您可以<a href="https://shedsevenn.lnk.to/AMOTPR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订/预保存专辑。</p><p>该乐队的英国巡演日期如下。请访问<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fshed-seven-tickets%2Fartist%2F776892" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>获取任何剩余门票。</p><p> <strong style="color: #111111; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 27px;">Shed Seven 在英国的日期如下：</strong></p></div><div><strong>十月</strong><strong style="color: #111111; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 27px;"><br /></strong></div><div><p> <strong>19 – 卡迪夫特兰希德</strong><br /><strong>20 – 伦敦 O2 牧羊人布什帝国</strong><br /><strong>21 - 诺丁汉摇滚城</strong><br /><strong>23 – Stoke Victoria Hall</strong><br /> <strong>24 – Wolverhampton Wulfrun Hall</strong><br /> <strong>26 – Glasgow Barrowland</strong><br /> <strong>27 – Middlesbrough Town Hall</strong><br /> <strong>28 – Manchester Albert Hall</strong></p></div><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shed-seven-share-new-single-featuring-rowetta-and-talk-guest-heavy-album-a-matter-of-time-3505094">Shed Seven share new single featuring Rowetta and talk guest-heavy album &#39;A Matter Of Time&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
 'Fortnite' developer Epic Games loses 830 employees in layoffs https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/fortnite-developer-epic-games-loses-830-employees-in-layoffs-3506388?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=fortnite-developer-epic-games-loses-830-employees-in-layoffsImogen Donovan Fri, 29 Sep 2023 08:58:39 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3506388 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/epic-games-announces-layoffs-affecting-16-per-cent-of-staff.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/epic-games-announces-layoffs-affecting-16-per-cent-of-staff.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/epic-games-announces-layoffs-affecting-16-per-cent-of-staff-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/epic-games-announces-layoffs-affecting-16-per-cent-of-staff-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/epic-games-announces-layoffs-affecting-16-per-cent-of-staff-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/epic-games-announces-layoffs-affecting-16-per-cent-of-staff-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/epic-games-announces-layoffs-affecting-16-per-cent-of-staff-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Through this, the company aims to &quot;[cut] costs without sacrificing development or lines of businesses&quot;</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/fortnite-developer-epic-games-loses-830-employees-in-layoffs-3506388">&#39;Fortnite&#39; developer Epic Games loses 830 employees in layoffs</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/epic-games-announces-layoffs-affecting-16-per-cent-of-staff.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/epic-games-announces-layoffs-affecting-16-per-cent-of-staff.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/epic-games-announces-layoffs-affecting-16-per-cent-of-staff-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/epic-games-announces-layoffs-affecting-16-per-cent-of-staff-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/epic-games-announces-layoffs-affecting-16-per-cent-of-staff-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/epic-games-announces-layoffs-affecting-16-per-cent-of-staff-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/epic-games-announces-layoffs-affecting-16-per-cent-of-staff-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/epic-games">Epic Games</a> has announced the loss of 830 employees in a round of layoffs, with “two-thirds” of these roles outside of game development ventures.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/best-upcoming-games-we-saw-at-gamescom-2023-3505950">Here are some of the best upcoming games we saw at Gamescom 2023</a></strong></li></ul><p> Through this, CEO Tim Sweeney aimed to “[cut] costs without sacrificing development or lines of businesses” and guarantee the continued efficacy of the company&#39;s development functions.</p><p> “For a while now, we&#39;ve been spending way more money than we earn, investing in the next evolution of Epic and growing <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/fortnite"><em>Fortnite</em></a> as a metaverse-inspired ecosystem for creators,” explained Sweeney in <a href="https://www.epicgames.com/site/en-US/news/layoffs-at-epic" target="_blank" rel="noopener">a post to the Epic Games official website</a> .</p><p> “I had long been optimistic that we could power through this transition without layoffs, but in retrospect I see that this was unrealistic.” </p><figure id="attachment_3496070" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3496070" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3496070" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fortnite-epic-games-donald-mustard.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fortnite-epic-games-donald-mustard.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fortnite-epic-games-donald-mustard-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fortnite-epic-games-donald-mustard-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fortnite-epic-games-donald-mustard-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fortnite-epic-games-donald-mustard-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fortnite-epic-games-donald-mustard-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3496070" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;Fortnite&#39; Credit: Epic Games</figcaption></figure><p> Of these 830 employees, Epic Games will lose 250 employees resulting from divestitures from Bandcamp and SuperAwesome. Bandcamp <a href="https://www.songtradr.com/blog/posts/songtradr-bandcamp-acquisition" target="_blank" rel="noopener">will be owned by Songtradr</a> and “most” of SuperAwesome <a href="https://www.superawesome.com/blog/superawesome-leadership-to-acquire-company-from-epic-games/">will be taken over by SuperAwesome Leadership</a> .</p><p> Those affected will benefit from a severance package that contains career transition services, visa support, six months base pay, the opportunity to “accelerate people&#39;s stock option vesting schedule through the end of 2024” and six months of Epic-paid healthcare in the United States, Canada and Brazil.</p><p> There will be no further redundancies in the future, affirmed Sweeney. On the topic of recruitment, the company said that it will hire for “critical roles while maintaining net-zero at our new size”.</p><p> Similarly, this week has seen the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/creative-assembly-shooter-hyenas-has-been-cancelled-by-sega-3505672">cancellation of Creative Assembly&#39;s <em>Hyenas</em></a> as <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/sega">Sega</a> Sammy forecasted “record losses of approximately 14.3billion yen [£78.6million]” in this fiscal year. </p><figure id="attachment_3429622" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3429622" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3429622" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fortnite-eren-jaeger-header.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fortnite-eren-jaeger-header.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fortnite-eren-jaeger-header-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fortnite-eren-jaeger-header-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fortnite-eren-jaeger-header-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fortnite-eren-jaeger-header-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fortnite-eren-jaeger-header-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3429622" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;Fortnite&#39; Credit: Epic Games</figcaption></figure><p> “Organisational changes” in <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/activision-blizzard">Activision Blizzard</a> &#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/hearthstone"><em>Hearthstone</em></a> team led to 10 developers being let go without notice, reported <a href="https://twitter.com/ethangach/status/1706835076615434323"><em>Kotaku</em></a> , and “aggressive growth targets” at <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/roblox-corporation">Roblox Corporation</a> required the <a href="https://www.gamesindustry.biz/roblox-lays-off-30-staff">loss of around 30 employees</a> in order to meet them.</p><p> In other gaming news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/cities-skylines-2"><em>Cities: Skylines 2</em></a> has been delayed for <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PS5</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a> so that the quality of the final experience is as polished as possible.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/fortnite-developer-epic-games-loses-830-employees-in-layoffs-3506388">&#39;Fortnite&#39; developer Epic Games loses 830 employees in layoffs</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
